#states/information

    MxN squares

    where the apple is

    where the snake is
        how long the snake is
        where each snake piece is, each individual one


#operations/methods

    movement of snake

    touching of the apple

    touching itself

    touching wall


#class suggestions

Data types

Snake - list of parts
Class Part : x, y, type(snake/apple/empty)
Apple - one part
Map - list of list of Parts
Game - current state of a game containing a Map, Apple, Snake, Board Size (x/y)



